# Test Validation Report

## 1. Executive Summary
This report documents the logical (not actually ran) validation of the automated unit tests (written in python) against the Wonderful and Mysterious Web Application. These are the theoritical results of the tests which would be executed within the Dockerized environment specified in the Test Plan.
With more time, I hope to actually run and execute the aforementioned tests against the Docker hosted application.

